welcome_message_body: "Welcome to East Rancho Dominguez, a charming city known for its rich history and vibrant culture. We invite you to explore and experience all that this beautiful city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Compton Airport provides services for commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Compton Airport is reserved for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Tom Bradley International Terminal
terminals.description: The main international terminal at LAX, serving a variety of international airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 1

terminals.name: Terminal 3

terminals.name: Terminal 4

terminals.name: Terminal 5

terminals.name: Terminal 6

terminals.name: Terminal 7

terminals.name: Terminal 8

wifi.note: Limited to 45 minutes per session. Premium WiFi packages available for purchase.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including shops, restaurants, and lounges.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Municipal Airport is dedicated to private and charter flights, providing a comfortable and convenient experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at El Monte Airport houses all check-in counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at El Monte Airport is dedicated to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, free of charge.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bob Hope Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal B

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport by selecting the network name and agreeing to the terms and conditions.
